`deploy.ps1` and `push.ps1` run the smoke check automatically before commit.

## Agent workflow

1. Read this file first.
2. `git checkout main && git pull origin main`
3. Create branch: `cursor/<description>-fb87`
4. Minimal diff — never replace all of `index.html`
5. Run smoke check locally
6. Bump SPA version (Extension only if `extension/` changed)
7. Ship via PR — **never push or merge to `main` directly**
8. After auto-merge: user pulls `main`, hard-refreshes SPA, reloads extension if needed

